    Worked on a few projects, mostly frontend in React, and also contributed a few lines of backend code in Node.`,
  },
  {
    year: '9/2021 - 12/2021',
    position: 'Front-End Developer',
    company: 'ATLAS GROUP',
    place: 'Ostrava, Czech Republic (on-site)',
